==English==

===Verb===
'''[[get]] [[taken]] [[in]]'''
#{{idiomatic}} To be [[fooled]]; to [[fall for]].
#:''I wonder how many people will '''get taken in''' by their addition of a fancy-looking front panel to a crummy device.''
